      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/graviton.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />&nbsp;</sub>Graviton Revelation<br />You can redirect the energy of deadly falls into deadlier strikes. You reduce falling damage you take by an amount equal to your solarian level (minimum 0 damage). If you hit a creature using a melee attack within 1 round of reducing your falling damage in this way, your first such successful attack deals additional damage equal to the falling damage this revelation prevented. When you are fully graviton attuned, add your Charisma modifier to the maximum falling damage this revelation can prevent.</p>"
